<title>UK: London silver fixes firmer backed by PGM strength.</title>
<headline>London silver fixes firmer backed by PGM strength.</headline>
<text>
<p>SILVER - Fixed at 525.25 cents vs 522.90 cents previously. Lifted by firmness in PGMs, gold. Quiet.</p>
<p>GOLD - Steady at $357.75/$358.05, up about $4.15.</p>
<p>PLATINUM - Sharply higher early. $393.75/$394.75, up $11.75 on buying against Norilsk strike threat.</p>
<p>PALLADIUM - Up $11.95 on Norilsk at $157.00/$158.00.</p>
